Initial Setup
=============

After cheking out, please do the following steps:

1) create eclipse projects for all plugins by running
$ ./gradlew eclipse

2) optional (to ensure better code quality):
setup git by running
$ cat > .git/hooks/pre-commit
#!/bin/bash

set -e
tools/spaces.sh --git
^D
$ chmod 755 .git/hooks/pre-commit

3) Test everything by running
$ export GRADLE_OPTS=-XX:MaxPermSize=512M
$ ./gradlew dist
and
$ ./gradlew start

run
$ ./gradlew
for a list of options
